What a fantastic -- and easy -- recipe! I made it for 6 guests for a Christmas Eve dinner, and it was a smash hit! Almost no prep time (more time to enjoy your guests) and I used the leftover chops to make pork sandwiches with dijon mustard and cilantro the next day. A crown roast recipe can seem overwhelming, but this one was so user-friendly, and yet still an elegant meal!

